# Example of an Anomaly Pattern
noria:AnomalyPattern_HighLatencyDNS a noria:AnomalyPattern ;
    rdfs:label "High Latency DNS Anomaly Pattern"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Pattern indicating a potential DNS resolution issue due to high network latency or server overload."@en ;
    folio:hasCause "Network congestion or DNS server overload."@en ;
    folio:hasEffect "Slow website loading, service unavailability."@en .

